Comment: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:06.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,————OPJP————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嫌いで {\fs60}I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ね 分かってる {\fs60}WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}女の子ってね {\fs60}YEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:37.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}突然変異で 恋の魔法にかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}どうにかして {\fs60}WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不安な気持ち {\fs60}YEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ピンクな風船 ふかふか飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君ならできる（きっと）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:55.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}方程式を（解いて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ハットを二乗 さらに掛けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}気持ちはお余りよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二人も出しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}素直に {\fs60}SAY YES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「私を好き」って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:07.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}認めて {\fs60}SAY YES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヤキモチは嫌なの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君じゃなきゃ ダメなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恋人以上 好き未満
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:17.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}答えは {\fs60}EASY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}早く導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:19.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}このまま {\fs60}TAKE IT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ピュア受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:28.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君が勇気を出したその日は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}キスくらいしていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}嫌いで {\fs60}I LOVE YOU
Comment: 1,0:22:06.59,0:22:06.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,————OPCN————
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.13,0:22:10.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}討厭卻又I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 你知道嗎 WOW
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}女孩子呀 YEAH
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.83,0:22:37.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天有不測 忽然間就中了戀愛的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快做些什麼 WOW
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不安的心情 YEAH
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}像粉色的氣球那般輕輕飛走
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果是你的話就可以做得到（一定）
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.85,0:22:55.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把方程式（解開）
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把心意平方後再相乘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}分量滿滿的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把我們兩個也加上去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}坦率地 SAY YES
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}說你喜歡我
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.90,0:23:07.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快承認吧 SAY YES
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要感情衝動
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是你的話就不可以
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戀人以上 喜歡未滿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.70,0:23:17.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}答案很 EASY
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快快順從心意
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.66,0:23:19.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就這樣 TAKE IT
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}接受這純潔的心意
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.17,0:23:28.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等到你鼓起勇氣的那一天
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}親吻你也可以哦
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}討厭卻又I LOVE YOU
